forge-voice-module-locked = The installed voice module cannot be reconfigured.
forge-voice-module-ui-name = voice module
transmutin-effect-popup = The body twists into a new humanoid shape!
forge-surgical-armor-already-installed = This body already has an armor implant installed.

reagent-effect-guidebook-transmutin-species-reaction = Converts transmutin into a donor-species transmutin when mixed with blood carrying species data.
reagent-effect-guidebook-transmutin-mutate-monkey = Mutates monkeys into the selected humanoid species without granting intelligence.

ent-ForgeVoiceModuleImplant = voice module implant
    .desc = A configurable subdermal TTS voice modulator. Configure it in hand before implantation.
ent-ForgeSubdermalArmorImplant = subdermal armor implant
    .desc = A surgical armor implant for the torso cavity. It reinforces the body against mechanical damage, but conducts heat dangerously well.
ent-ForgeReflectiveSubdermalArmorImplant = reflective subdermal armor implant
    .desc = A surgical armor implant for the torso cavity. Reflective heat sinks resist temperature extremes, but make impacts bite harder.
ent-ForgeMilLeftHand = M.I.L left hand
    .desc = A cybernetic left hand with wrist micro-actuators that add force to unarmed strikes.
ent-ForgeMilRightHand = M.I.L right hand
    .desc = A cybernetic right hand with wrist micro-actuators that add force to unarmed strikes.
ent-ForgeRiplyLeftHand = R.I.P.L.Y left hand
    .desc = A cybernetic left hand with reinforced fingertip anchors. It helps drag and carry heavy bodies only when paired with the matching hand.
ent-ForgeRiplyRightHand = R.I.P.L.Y right hand
    .desc = A cybernetic right hand with reinforced fingertip anchors. It helps drag and carry heavy bodies only when paired with the matching hand.
ent-ForgeVoiceModuleImplanter = voice module implanter
    .desc = A disposable syringe preloaded with a configurable voice module implant.
ent-ForgeCyberneticLiver = cybernetic liver
    .desc = A reinforced liver module that slowly filters toxins from the bloodstream.
ent-ForgeCyberneticKidneys = cybernetic kidneys
    .desc = A pair of cybernetic kidneys that gradually purge radiation damage.
ent-ForgeSpaceKangarooLungs = space kangaroo lungs
    .desc = Elastic alien lungs that oxygenate muscles well enough to make movement easier.
ent-ForgeSpaceTickLiver = space tick liver
    .desc = A suspiciously predatory liver that routes a tiny dose of toxin into barehanded hits.
ent-BioSynthKidneys = bio-synthetic kidneys
    .desc = These kidneys can be transplanted into any living organism and they will adapt to their recipient.
ent-ForgeBioSynthTorso = bio-synthetic torso
    .desc = A printed human torso for cases where very little of the patient is left.
ent-ForgeTransmutinChemistryBottle = transmutin bottle
    .desc = A small bottle containing 30 units of transmutin.

